example.good case:
带有 @permission 标签，同时在接口声明中显式列出了 201 错误码，实现中在权限校验失败时向开发者返回了 201。

```C++
/**
 * @permission ohos.permission.SYSTEM_FLOAT_WINDOW
 * @throws { BusinessError } 201 - Permission denied. An application does not have the permission to call the API.
 */
function createWindow(config: Configuration): Window;

napi_value NapiCreateWindow(napi_env env, napi_callback_info info)
{
    uint64_t tokenId = AccessTokenHelper::GetCallingTokenID();
    bool hasPermission = AccessTokenHelper::VerifyAccessToken(tokenId, "ohos.permission.SYSTEM_FLOAT_WINDOW");
    if (!hasPermission) {
        napi_throw(env, JsErrUtils::CreateJsError(env, 201, "Permission denied."));
        return NapiGetUndefined(env);
    }
    return CreateWindow(env, info);
}
```

