example.good case:
API 依赖真实设备硬件能力，文档声明了 801，实现中在硬件能力不支持时返回了 801。

```C++
/**
 * @throws { BusinessError } 801 - Capability not supported.
 * @since 23 static
 */
function onOrientationChange(callback: Callback<OrientationResponse>, options?: Options): void;

napi_value OrientationChange(napi_env env, napi_callback_info info)
{
    if (!checkDeviceSupport()) {
        napi_throw_error(env, "801", "Capability not supported.");
        return NapiGetUndefined(env);
    }
    return doOrientationChange(env, info);
}
```

